summary: This removes a lot of clutter from Breezehome in Whiterun to improve performance whilst inside.
descriptionHtml:
This mod will remove alot of clutter and [u]un-needed[/u] objects from the main room and other places.

- This mod [u]WILL[/u] make Breezehome very bland in some areas. They may not be lighted aswell.

- I [u]HAVE[/u] In return, added chests on the bottom floor where a shelf used to be and under the stairs, for extra storage. :)

- This is my first mod.

- [u]PLEASE[/u] Report bugs.
author: Tame Cat
